Start Point: Talk to Maurice Jondrell, in the Eldergleam Sanctuary

Official Difficulty: Novice

Description: Maurice Jondrell wishes to become an alchemist to protect the Eldergleam, but requires your assistance in obtaining a large amount of ingredients to kickstart his career.

Official length: Very Short

Requirements: None

Items required: 
- Bear Pelt
- Skeever Tail
- Cow Hide
- Chicken Breast

Enemies to defeat: 
- Bear
- Skeever
- Cow
- Chicken

Quest Stages: 

Rewards: 
1 Alchemy Level
